"Rudi ne rangili re vaahlaa taari vaansali re lol"
Never heard such a power rendition of our Gujarati Folk song... there are many more such songs, wish musicians like Salim - Sulaiman bring forward such rich songs out to the masses....

Exceptional flute playing by Paras Nath, awesome super awesome towards the cresendo... Nothing less than power vocal by Karsan Sagthia...

Hope to hear new renditions this Navratri..... get your dandiyas and gears ready...
